		<title>Mayo Clinic discovers new role for protein to fight tumors</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-discovers-new-role-for-protein-to-fight-tumors/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Colette Gallagher]]></dc:creator>
